Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.73,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:41.01,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Chase\Nof the Little Detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the golden Angel Statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:01:58.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:01.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.\NThat's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the country's\Nfinest treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing else like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the way! Get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:31.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:58.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to solve crimes\Nreally excite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty! Tonight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As you all know, there's enough\Ngold in that Angel Statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:19.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,to provide the weapons needed\Nto destroy an entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever's necessary\Nto keep it from Moriarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Moriarty been delayed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you mention in your warning\Nthat you would come from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:13.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know the true genius of\Ncrime that Professor Moriarty is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:25.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:29.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give a reward\Nto whoever catches him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't let him get\Naway with the Angel Statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the symbol of our nation's peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Inspector Lestrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:50.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's leading a suicide squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the wind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your suicide squad efforts\Nare down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck on your way back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you! Wait a sec! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pull me up will ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:13.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What! Hey, wait!\NYou don't have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:30.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to go around\Nand take the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:55.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, don't linger!\NPlease land quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:05.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:20.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I am immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and hide the Angel Statue\Nat the prepared site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:30.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is from the\Nsouth-east with a 3.2 velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind has died down\Nbut maintains the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're hurrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the contents of\Nevery carriage thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is depending\Non this police cordon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,to cover the entire city of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let even a\Nsingle ant sneak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is to\Nwait until the heat is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hide in the warehouse and stake\Nout quietly until Moriarty arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:20.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no trace of the carriage,\Neven after a thorough search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Angel Statue must be hidden\Naround here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean they'll\Ncome back to get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:10.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I landed on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool us!\NWe know you're one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,To whom are you referring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go on our dream adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,once we've installed\Nthis engine on our boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:49.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:50.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they gone up in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Or down underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:09.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't get back the Angel Statue,\Nmy life as an inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop searching where\Nthere's nothing to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Move on to the next location!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:17.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:17.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:30.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The cops withdrew so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Lestrade's head is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's an inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:41.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, empty, empty,\Ncompletely empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:45.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they didn't find our\Nhiding place for the Angel Statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My brain is the best in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can match...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe one person can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:56.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:57.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be scared of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:58.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, why are you\Ngoing along with these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said "them", you meant\NProfessor Moriarty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Moriarty come down\Nin that balloon, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still trying to act innocent\Nafter messing up our playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty's come\Nhere that many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:26.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps in preparation of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:27.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in close and grab him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rescue him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:56.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears Moriarty has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet? Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:14.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:45.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You rascals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume I'll go easy on you\Njust 'cause you're little kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:56.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:58.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:07.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You little!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the hostage\Nas a last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:33.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,While the Professor was dancing,\NI saved the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smarty pants Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:14.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, it's true you're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:16.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You were brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys should have courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Two members are missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still on that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:32.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After them! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After them? We've no boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:38.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You have your boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, will you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:41.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disaster, eh Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter so long as\Nwe get what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no boat to come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the treasure is all ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:02.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go save your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:42.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:43.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we catch up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! Check it out, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, this engine is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep it well tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drive you straight into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What do those fools\Nthink they're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, you take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:44.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You overly persistent pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,More power from the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,With this wrecked engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and do what I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:10.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:54.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:10.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they've hidden the Angel Statue\Nsomewhere on this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:14.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:18.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:26.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not on deck or in the hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it must be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:38.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:50.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we busted your car!\NWe'll give you the engine back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just consider it a present\Nto help fulfil your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:05.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:09.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, you can take both of us\Non your next adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:13.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure thing!\NYou'll definitely come with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:15.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:18.28,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:19.82,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, thanks Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:20.95,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks Mister!
