Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.08,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,After solving a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:02.75,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes and I wandered into an old\Nmansion where a dark plot was brewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:05.51,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,What impending danger waits\Nfor the beautiful lady of the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.92,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is the frightening\Nsecret of a dotted rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:15.76,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
